        <seg>洌彼下泉，浸彼苞稂。愾我寤嘆，念彼周京。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Cold come the waters down from that spring,
* And overflow the bushy wolfs-tail grass
Ah me! I awake and sigh,
Thinking of that capital of Chow.</seg>
